title: SUPERAntiSpyware Professional 5.7.1014 + Key - CORE
description:
Description:
SUPERAntiSpyware Professional is a useful and powerful program that will detect and remove Spyware, Adware, Malware, Trojans, KeyLoggers, Dialers, Hi-Jackers, and Worms.
SUPERAntiSpyware features many unique and powerful technologies and removes spyware threats that other applications fail to remove.


What's New in version 5.7.1014 (18th Dec, 2013) :
-Identification of potentially unwanted programs and secure removal.
-Places key tools, such as quarantine management, scan logs, and repair features in one place with a cleaner toolkit interface.
-Streamlines self-service licensing for an easier path to retrieving and resetting license keys.
-Added SUPERDelete file removal to the context menu in explorer.
-More robust persistent file removal management.
